title: Minecraft, But If You Laugh You Lose...
author: GeorgeNotFound
description:
Minecraft, But If You Laugh You Lose... This video is hilarious!
My friends have to do whatever they can to make me laugh. If they can make me laugh 3 times, they win. If I beat the game before they make me laugh 3 times, I win!

This was absolutely the funniest video ever.
